{"data": [{"id": "4745780", "title": "Glaukos: Still Bullish, But Embedded Expectations Are Now High", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business on Wall Street in Manhattan\" data-id=\"1220627489\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6240px\" height=\"4160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Pgiam/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Update</h2> <p>Following <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4632479-glaukos-continued-growth-rates-regulatory-tailwinds-and-support\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4632479-glaukos-continued-growth-rates-regulatory-tailwinds-and-support\" target=\"_blank\">my last publication</a> on Glaukos Corporation (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GKOS#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GKOS#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" target=\"_blank\">GKOS</a>) in August FY'23 the stock is +90% and taken out additional price objectives along the way. The business is now valued &gt;12x book and 9x EV/IC as investors realize the value of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745780-glaukos-still-bullish-but-embedded-expectations-are-now-high", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 15:04:19", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745779", "title": "Sable Offshore Offers Convexity For 2025", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/dv789006/photo/brent-oil-field-production-platforms-north-sea-uk.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=VCeNmxZhtV4kmeNv_LstvGNI9UIMFgAhcRVXxRwuM9A=\" alt=\"Brent Oil Field, Production Platforms, North Sea, UK\" data-id=\"dv789006\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Michael Saint Maur Sheil/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Sable Offshore (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SOC\" title=\"Sable Offshore Corp.\">SOC</a></span>) is a risky former SPAC that holds the rights to an oil production complex off the coast of California. All activities were shut down after a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Refugio_oil_spill\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Refugio_oil_spill\" target=\"_blank\">pipeline spill in 2015. </a>There has been much back</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745779-sable-offshore-offers-convexity-for-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 14:54:33", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745778", "title": "XDIV: A Quality Dividend Fund With Sector-Specific Risks And Limited Growth Potential", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183890877/image_183890877.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Red Maple\" data-id=\"183890877\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1020px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183890877/image_183890877.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183890877/image_183890877.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183890877/image_183890877.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183890877/image_183890877.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183890877/image_183890877.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183890877/image_183890877.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183890877/image_183890877.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183890877/image_183890877.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Martin Wahlborg</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>ETF Overview</h2> <p>iShares Core MSCI Canadian Quality Dividend Index ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">TSX:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XDIV:CA\" title=\"iShares Core MSCI Canadian Quality Dividend Index ETF\">XDIV:CA</a></span>) invests in a portfolio of quality dividend stocks in Canada. The fund\u2019s management expense ratio of 0.11% is cheap. Funds such as iShares S&amp;P/TSX Composite High Dividend Index</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183890877/image_183890877.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745778-xdiv-a-quality-dividend-fund-with-sector-specific-risks-and-limited-growth-potential", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 14:33:18", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745781", "title": "Stacking The Deck Trading In FX, Crypto, And Capital Markets", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1920653372/image_1920653372.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young business people having stock trading and investing course\" data-id=\"1920653372\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1920653372/image_1920653372.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1920653372/image_1920653372.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1920653372/image_1920653372.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1920653372/image_1920653372.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1920653372/image_1920653372.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1920653372/image_1920653372.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1920653372/image_1920653372.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1920653372/image_1920653372.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">ilkercelik/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Mike Larson</em></p> <h2>Transcript</h2> <p><strong>Larson -</strong> The currency markets are in flux. And that's true whether you're talking about the traditional FX market or the cryptocurrency space. Among the more noteworthy recent trends: The US dollar has soared in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1920653372/image_1920653372.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745781-stacking-deck-trading-fx-crypto-capital-markets", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 14:30:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745776", "title": "Darden Restaurants: Improved Outlook, But Valuation Don't Look Cheap (Rating Upgrade To Hold)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2050787216/image_2050787216.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Joyful Brunch Amongst Urban Friends\" data-id=\"2050787216\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2050787216/image_2050787216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2050787216/image_2050787216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2050787216/image_2050787216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2050787216/image_2050787216.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2050787216/image_2050787216.jpg?io=getty-c-w640