ee Resources: A Copper/Gold Opportunity In Mongolia", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1184341328/image_1184341328.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Portrait of eagle hunter standing in desert in Mongolia\" data-id=\"1184341328\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1184341328/image_1184341328.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1184341328/image_1184341328.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1184341328/image_1184341328.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1184341328/image_1184341328.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1184341328/image_1184341328.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1184341328/image_1184341328.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1184341328/image_1184341328.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1184341328/image_1184341328.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Oleh_Slobodeniuk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>Entree Resources Ltd (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ERLFF\" title=\"Entr\u00e9e Resources Ltd.\">OTCQB:ERLFF</a>) is a small cap Canadian miner in a joint venture partnership with a participating interest in the Oyu Tolgoi copper/gold mining project in Mongolia. This project is about a 10-hour drive from the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1184341328/image_1184341328.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745772-entree-resources-a-coppergold-opportunity-in-mongolia", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 13:55:56", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745771", "title": "CEF Weekly Review: The Difficulties Of High-Quality CEFs", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A double exposure image of skyscrapers with overlay of financial graphs, set against a blurred background, illustrating the concept of business growth\" data-id=\"2159126735\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p clas